{"tid":412217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國新歌聲」<圖> 拒 當 中 國  台 灣 大 學","createTime":"2017-09-24T12:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T11:02:20.000Z","uid":35790,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da2cd76cb58f8a1303cc3fd6aac2ded40f9a19ee","tid":412217,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"中國新歌聲台大登場 獨派、台大生抗議 校方：終止演出<br />\n<br />\n2017-09-24 17:05<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2203211_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2203211_3.jpg&h=3438b998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔記者周彥妤／台北報導〕2017「中國新歌聲」上海．台北音樂節演唱會今於台大田徑場登場，獨派團體不滿台灣主體權益受損，集結抗議，先在場外與工作人員爆發口角衝突，隨後衝進場內，場面一片混亂，不久台大學生也入內抗議，中途主持人宣布校方基於安全考量，決定立即終止演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n獨派團體場外持票欲入場，遭工作人員以人牆阻擋，雙方爆發激烈衝突，獨派人士高喊「這是台灣人的土地，台灣人有票為什麼不可以進去！」隨後隨後衝進場內，進去現場高舉台灣旗、鳴汽笛，另手持抗議標語「拒當中國台灣大學」、「枉顧學生為統戰」。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，台大學生也進去現場抗議，邊鳴汽笛、撒冥紙，手持標語「市府上下其手吃人夠夠」，高喊「還我操場」，要求文化局、台大校方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n中途，主持人宣布，校方基於安全考量，決定立即終止演唱會。學生一陣歡呼，隨後學生登上舞台高喊，「我們是台灣大學，不是中國台灣大學」，「譴責柯文哲，校方要負責」，「台大吃人夠夠，市府上下其手」，「統戰活動退出校園」，嚴正表達抗議訴求。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2203211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2203211&d=%2Bp63jj8WsA59aZCZI4ezURxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=fa0d29b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2203211&h=c4a23d6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2203211</a>"},{"pid":"7cf3b6e934fd7f7d63d9acf1cf825738c67ad8df","tid":412217,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d4ba556b31cbfdce984acf8f0556182bf5a667","tid":412217,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acc7cc00ba54964146bfc585c10f2f3c45857ec","tid":412217,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c13503045eea3d66b08bb7070779b678a84dc5","tid":412217,"uid":141461,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"你的確是中華民國(中國)台灣大學"},{"pid":"4bd8eb885e73ca2170b987b8ea881521e26214ea","tid":412217,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac18680bc926530f084a67202291173d687399e3","tid":412217,"uid":104092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"聽講有學生比人打到流血"},{"pid":"3faf8fc8825b17ffcee81fa2be92683ec3fa38a7","tid":412217,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講有學生比人打到流血</blockquote><br />\n今早cctvb只報台上表演者<br />\n被一個小鐵罐跌親(慢鏡)<br />\n隻字無提有親中團體成員追打大學生"},{"pid":"f135fc286c0bedd92eec9d01dab59d39936ed878","tid":412217,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"班學生點解唔還拖？"}]}